        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那么好吃的菜，想不记得才难吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "得亏有我，不然你现在只能记住一百种泡面的味道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她刚说完，泡面那股咸腻立刻涌进我的鼻腔，连同那段忙得晕头转向的日子一起浮现在眼前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在处理不完的工作面前，吃饭便成了负担。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我找来一碗泡面，准备随便应付两口，顺带把脑子里的弦松一松。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "宿舍大厅空旷而安静，袅袅热气在惨白的灯光下显得有些寂寞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "直到端着养生茶壶的肴慢悠悠地路过，又小退几步回到我面前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "诶？分析员？你怎么在这里吃上泡面了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "懒得去餐厅了，随便对付两口。要尝尝吗？泡椒味的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
